berbagi rasa sakitmu, ibu.

00:13:40.360 --> 00:13:41.400
Ayah.

00:13:43.520 --> 00:13:44.440
Chhavi.

00:13:45.200 --> 00:13:48.080
Aku... aku perlu bicara denganmu.

00:13:49.360 --> 00:13:51.040
Ya.  Katakan padaku, sayang.

00:13:56.240 --> 00:13:58.840
'Aparajita dan putri-putrinya
harus meninggalkan rumah.'

